Class AddressList

  • java.lang.Object
    • AddressList

  • public class AddressList
extends java.lang.Object
    AddressList.java - Contains the data and methods for a singly linked list of contact list data. Gives the user ability to add new contacts, search the list, and manipulate existing data within the list.
    Version:
    11/19/15
    Author:
    Justin Watts
